      • validateEditLog

        static FSEditLogLoader.EditLogValidation validateEditLog(EditLogInputStream in)
        Find the last valid transaction ID in the stream. If there are invalid or corrupt transactions in the middle of the stream, validateEditLog will skip over them. This reads through the stream but does not close it.

      • createStartupProgressStep

        private static Step createStartupProgressStep(EditLogInputStream edits)
                                       throws IOException
        Creates a Step used for updating startup progress, populated with information from the given edits. The step always includes the log's name. If the log has a known length, then the length is included in the step too.
        Parameters:
        edits - EditLogInputStream to use for populating step
        Returns:
        Step populated with information from edits
        Throws:
        IOException - thrown if there is an I/O error
